<task id="task_1490B2E462404C8F98ACED3B2C37628D">
  <title>Associate Mbox-Specific Parameters</title>
  <shortdesc>Parameters can be added and associated with an mbox. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <steps id="steps_1B2CBE846ECE4100A668E4FE25A822B8">
      <step id="step_FB2A42DDFEB14B3CA776A431BF1A21F3">
        <cmd>Follow the instructions for a inserting 
			 <xref href="t_Creating_a_Single_Mbox.xml#task_FE6BEB3A1264493A9E9A4CFC5023CCA9" type="task" format="dita" scope="local">a basic mbox</xref>. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_1D2C6C99F086411B9F389B0A1EC7FEC6">
        <cmd>After the mbox title, enter the parameters and values you wish to
			 add to the mbox. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>Parameters and values are case sensitive. Match the case of the
				parameters and values you will receive during the campaign or test. 
			 </p>
          <p>Parameters use the structure shown below: 
			 </p>
          <p>
            <codeblock outputclass="syntax html">&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;

mboxCreate('myMbox',"parameter1=value1",​"parameter2=value2","parameter3=value3");

&lt;/script&gt;</codeblock>
          </p>
          <p>For example: 
			 </p>
          <p>
            <codeblock outputclass="syntax html">&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;

mboxCreate('myMbox',"state=AL",​​"categoryId=toys, books, accessories");

&lt;/script&gt;</codeblock>
          </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
